                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item>
                           <label>Inscription:</label> <locus from="ia">right flyleaf (f. ia)</locus> describes the work and states the name of former owner George William Hamilton in Persian, probably in the hand of his assistant <persName role="ins" key="person_f6587">Muhīn Dās</persName>:
                           <q xml:lang="fa">
                              تاریخ ندا بعد از رحلت عالمگیر بادشاه آنچه روداد. کرنیل جارج ولیم هملتن صاحب بهادر.
